description: Exceptional restaurant for Turkish food. The space is really spacious where many seats are available. They have indoor and outdoor seats. The service was 10/10 and the food was well-prepared and nicely served. I ordered florya salad based on the waiter‚Äôs recommendation and I truly cannot fault it, literally delicious and unusual. Mini cheese kofta was nice also and generously stuffed with cheese. I also had Dallas steak it was a bit cold but was well-cooked. Baba ghanooj was also tasty and worth trying. They kindly served us with free tea and ginger shot. One last thing, it was a bit pricey but the quality of food served worth it. Highly recommended indeed.
restaurant_name: Florya Steak Lounge by et√ßi Mehmet
